- What difference does it make?

126
00:12:12,293 --> 00:12:15,285
Look, you better go back
to the nightclub and practice dancing.

127
00:12:15,453 --> 00:12:19,526
I'll meet you for dinner. And don't
you worry about not being a big hit.

128
00:12:19,693 --> 00:12:21,763
I'll shoot anyone
who doesn't like you.

129
00:12:21,973 --> 00:12:24,885
Okay, kid.

130
00:12:27,853 --> 00:12:29,525
