Mr. Laurel...

136
00:12:41,293 --> 00:12:45,286
...I want you to think very carefully
before answering my next question.

137
00:12:45,453 --> 00:12:48,729
Are you positive that this is the man
you identify...

138
00:12:48,893 --> 00:12:51,771
...as the one who committed the crime?
It is quite important...

139
00:12:51,933 --> 00:12:54,163
...that you answer
my question without prejudice.

140
00:12:54,333 --> 00:12:56,005
Are you positive?

141
00:13:00,613 --> 00:13:05,050
I'm positive
that I'm absolutely positive.

142
00:13:11,173 --> 00:13:14,848
- Order in the court.
- I'm sorry, Your Honor...

143
00:13:15,013 --> 00:13:17,925
...but I'm positively more positive...

144
00:13:18,133 --> 00:13:19,646
...than he is positive.

145
00:13:19,853 --> 00:13:21,684
Sit down, Mr. Hardy.

146
00:13:27,613 --> 00:13:28,841
LAWYER:
Your Honor...

147
00:13:29,053 --> 00:13:30,805
...that makes it doubly conclusive.

148
00:13:30,973 --> 00:13:32,691
That closes the case.

149
00:13:32,853 --> 00:13:34,650
Gentlemen of the jury...

150
00:13:34,853 --> 00:13:37,686
...I leave the matter
entirely in your hands.

151
00:13:37,893 --> 00:13:39,167
You've heard the evidence...

152
00:13:39,333 --> 00:13:42,245
...the arguments by counsel
and last witness in rebuttal.

153
00:13:42,413 --> 00:13:44,244
You may now retire.

154
00:13:44,413 --> 00:13:47,325
- Your Honor, we've reached our verdict.
- Guilty!

155
00:13:47,533 --> 00:13:49,444
You've convicted an innocent man!

156
00:13:49,613 --> 00:13:51,410
I sentence you
to 20 years, hard labor.

157
00:13:51,573 --> 00:13:53,803
I'm innocent, Your Honor,
I'm innocent!

158
00:13:56,533 --> 00:13:58,364
I'll get you two guys...

159
00:13:58,533 --> 00:14:01,331
...if it's the last thing I ever do.

160
00:14:01,613 --> 00:14:04,685
- Ha-ha-ha-ha...
- Ha!

161
00:14:07,733 --> 00:14:10,247
COLEMAN: So you served 20 years
at hard labor, huh?

162
00:14:10,453 --> 00:14:11,522
No.

163
