- Now pull yourself together.
- Welcome to Mexico City.

185
00:15:57,573 --> 00:15:59,211
- Thank you.
- And to you too, sir.

186
00:15:59,373 --> 00:16:01,204
- Thank you, sir.
- When did you arrive?

187
