- We got in this morning.
- Why didn't you let me know?

188
00:16:04,133 --> 00:16:06,169
- What for?
- What for?

189
00:16:06,333 --> 00:16:07,971
I've got you billed over this town.

190
00:16:08,133 --> 00:16:11,648
Don Sebastian, the greatest bullfighter
in the world from Barcelona, Spain.

191
00:16:11,813 --> 00:16:13,292
I'm afraid you're mistaken, sir.

192
00:16:13,453 --> 00:16:15,887
I'm Mr. Hardy,
and this is my good friend, Mr. Laurel.

193
00:16:16,053 --> 00:16:18,009
- How do you do?
- How do you do?

194
00:16:18,213 --> 00:16:21,808
Do you mean you're not Don Sebastian,
the great bullfighter from Barcelona?

195
00:16:21,973 --> 00:16:24,533
Why no, sir, we've never been
in Barcelona in our lives.

196
00:16:24,693 --> 00:16:27,082
- No?
- We come from Peoria.

197
